annotationA: Nitrilase and fragile histidine triad fusion protein NitFhit; Cleaves A-5'-PPP-5'A to yield AMP and ADP
annotationB: Iron regulatory protein 1B (Irp-1B) is a cytosolic aconitase. Although highly homologous to Irp-1A, the ability of Irp-1B to bind to highly conserved Iron Regulatory Elements has been questioned; Belongs to the aconitase/IPM isomerase family
